Andreas Schwab wrote:
> Except for bootup, how often do you need to mount more than one disk in
> parallel?
Only during bootup.  But it can be a significant portion of booting
time.  (The BIOS typically taking the other significant portion).
(Ok, I don't think it's _that_ significant and I've never bothered with
parallel mounts myself.  Then again I've never had more than 2 drives
connected).
